<!-- END CLASS="TEXTSIZE" -->
                        <span class="date">December 7, 2011</span>                         
                     </div>
                     <p>The mission of <em>America's Test Kitchen</em> is simple: to make "recipes that work." The syndicated PBS cooking show, hosted by Christopher Kimball, simplifies recipes in ways that home chefs can easily replicate with a fairly high degree of success.</p>                     <div class="container con1-5col nobar" id="con143275599">
                                                <div id="res143275616" class="bucketwrap photo218">
                                                      <a href="/books/titles/143275572/cooks-illustrated-cookbook-2-000-recipes-from-20-years-of-americas-most-trusted-"><img src="http://media.npr.org/assets/bakertaylor/covers/c/cooks-illustrated-cookbook/9781933615899_custom.jpg?t=1323278831&amp;s=15" width="218" class="img218" title="Cook's Illustrated Cookbook" alt="Cook's Illustrated Cookbook" /></a>                           <div class="captionwrap">
                                                            <p></p>
                           </div>
                           
<!-- END CLASS="CAPTIONWRAP" -->
                        </div>
                        <div id="res143275588" class="bucketwrap bookedition">
                                                      <h6><a href="http://www.npr.org/books/titles/143275572/cooks-illustrated-cookbook-2-000-recipes-from-20-years-of-americas-most-trusted-">Cook's Illustrated Cookbook</a></h6>
                           <p>2,000 Recipes from 20 Years of America's Most Trusted Cooking Magazine</p>                           <p class="author">by <a href="http://www.npr.org/books/authors/137956037/americas-test-kitchen"><span>America's Test Kitchen</span></a> and <a href="http://www.npr.org/books/authors/143275580/john-burgoyne"><span>John Burgoyne</span></a></p>                           <div class="bookinfo">
                                                            <p>Hardcover, 890 pages <span class="pipe">|</span> <a href="#" class="purchase">purchase</a></p>                              <div class="ecommercepop">
