                                    <li><span class="title">Fresh Food</span><a href="javascript: void(0);" class="podicon"></a><a href="http://www.npr.org/rss/rss.php?id=139002011" class="rssicon"></a><div class="podbox" style="display:none;">
      <p>Subscribe to <span>Fresh Food</span> podcast via:</p>   <p><a href="itpc://www.npr.org/templates/rss/podlayer.php?id=139002011" class="subitunes"><img src="http://media.npr.org/images/podcasts/ui/icon_itunes.gif" width="72" height="28" alt="iTunes" /></a><a href="zune://subscribe/?Fresh Food=http://www.npr.org/templates/rss/podlayer.php?id=139002011" class="subzune"><img src="http://media.npr.org/images/podcasts/ui/icon_zune.gif" width="56" height="28" alt="Zune" /></a></p>   <p class="divider">Or use this URL:</p>   <p><a class="podurllink" href="http://www.npr.org/templates/rss/podlayer.php?id=139002011"><img src="http://media.npr.org/images/podcasts/ui/icon_pod.gif" width="21" height="21" alt="This podcast" /></a><input type="text" class="podurl" value="http://www.npr.org/templates/rss/podlayer.php?id=139002011"></input>
